{"ts":"2026-03-01T16:42:42.179Z","type":"chat.output","payload":{"threadId":"session-1772382718772-a2wkybrkn","event":{"type":"cli","catId":"gemini","text":"哇！这个想法很有趣，1+1 等于几？从创意设计的角度来看，它可不仅仅是简单的数字相加哦！\n\n想象一下，当我们把两个独立的元素（比如，两个创意点子，或者两个视觉图形）“加”在一起时，我们期待"}},"meta":{"requestId":"949b0043-6ecb-4214-b39a-fd8ae89a001e","runId":"fc983e3e-7c07-40f0-b88e-a81755a46ab0","pid":84354,"cwd":"/Users/qiliangli/Documents/Coding/ateam","node":"v24.13.0","platform":"darwin","hostname":"liqiliangdeMacBook-Air-2.local"}}
